3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - Caching is also used in artificial intelligence to optimize memory usage. The paper's results on the complexity of general caching can be useful in designing efficient caching algorithms for AI applications. 
4. cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) - The paper presents NP-hardness results for general caching, which is a problem in discrete mathematics.
